VF-BI002: Big argument type mismatch
Phase: semantic
Location: line 6, column 44
Found: Integer
Expected: argument 2 as BigInteger for Big.addInt
Hint:
Big built-in arguments must match the exact arbitrary-precision type expected by the operation.

Use BigInteger values for Big.*Int operations and BigFloat values for Big.*Float operations.
Convert explicitly with Big.fromInteger or Big.floatFromInteger.
